  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Grease and flour an 8-inch round cake pan.",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together almond meal, sugar, and salt.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together egg whites and melted butter.",
    "Add almond extract to egg mixture and whisk to combine.",
    "Add wet ingredients to dry ingredients and mix until well combined.",
    "Pour batter into prepared cake pan and smooth top.",
    "Bake for 25-30 minutes or until a toothpick inserted in the center comes out clean.",
    "While cake is baking, prepare crumble topping."
